annotationA: Enhancer of yellow 1 is a TAF9 protein and a main component of the Transcription factor II D (TFIID) complex. TFIID is involved in recruiting the transcription machinery to core promoters and organizing specific enhancer-promoter interactions
annotationB: TBP-related factor (Trf) is ubiquitiously expressed but upregulated in the central nervous system and the gonads of developing Drosophila. In flies the majority of Trf substitutes for Tbp in Pol III transcription in complex with Brf. The rest of Trf initiates transcription of a small subset of PolII-transcribed genes regulating fly fertility and nervous system function
